# 📊 Mutual Fund Analysis Dashboard

## 📌 Overview

This project analyzes Indian mutual fund data using Python, Pandas, and live NAV APIs.  
It includes data ingestion, cleaning, analysis, and visualization of top mutual fund schemes.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📥 Automated data ingestion from CSV datasets
- 🌐 Live NAV data fetch using MFAPI
- 📊 Fund performance analysis
- 🏦 Comparison of top bluechip mutual funds
- 🧠 Data quality validation (AMFI code verification)
- 📈 Interactive dashboard (planned/optional)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly
- Requests (API calls)
- SQL (basic analysis)
- Jupyter Notebook

---

## 📂 Project Structure

